body:
While verilating modport with clocking block I got unsupported error as attached in screen shot. Here's the command that I ran:
`verilator --cc --timing -j 0 clocking.sv`

clocking.sv contains following code:

```
module sample; 
logic clk;
  intf vif(clk);
  
  initial begin
    $display("----------------------");
  $display("Interface Instantiated");
       $display("----------------------");
  end
  
endmodule

interface intf(input bit clk);

logic en,ack;

clocking cb @(posedge clk);
  default input #1 output #2;
    output en;
    input ack;    
  endclocking
  
   modport tb(clocking cb, input clk);
  modport RTL(output en,input ack);
  
  endinterface
```
Here is the output of command:
